What is the simplified value of $\frac{\sqrt{24}}{\sqrt{30}}\div\frac{\sqrt{20}}{3\sqrt{25}}$? ||| \begin{align*}
\frac{\sqrt{24}}{\sqrt{30}}\div\frac{\sqrt{20}}{3\sqrt{25}}&=\frac{\sqrt{24}}{\sqrt{30}}\times\frac{\sqrt{25}}{\sqrt{20}}\times 3 \\
&=\frac{2\sqrt{6}}{\sqrt{5}}\times 3 \times\frac{5}{\sqrt{20}} \\
&=3 \times 2 = 6 \\ 
&= \boxed{6} 
\end{align*}

